ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: We take turns presenting papers, and participate in discussions of the papers. I would recommend it to someone wanting more practice at presenting.
yes, I recommend it to other students
A seminar course where you were to present scientific material as you would for a meeting/job interview. I would not because I do not feel like I learned much more than I did going in.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I will need to present many times in the future, so it is a relevant course.
It made me much more comfortable with giving scientific presentations and critically reading papers.
I learned about neural electrophysiology which I had not been exposed to previously much.It did not contribute really to my dissertation research.
